message.text:
“Pang matalino lang diyan, kinakabahan ako!” 😣

Hi IABF!🌞 STRAW Internal Affairs can sound intimidating at first — lalo na kapag narinig mo na connected kami with the House of Representatives, Congress, plus petition writing and resolutions 😳.

Pero real talk? Once I joined, I realized na kung gaano karami ang terminologies, ganoon din karami ang platforms where we can lobby, voice out, and address our concerns within the campus.

To be honest, joining my home division was one of the best decisions I’ve ever made. I came in as a freshie with zero knowledge, pero my seniors, Direks, and OICs guided me every step of the way. It turned out not just manageable — but actually fun to serve and help the rest of the IABF community🥹🫶🏻

Kaya naman if you’ve been thinking about it… this is your sign 👀✨ JOIN US!
We’ll be here to welcome you with open arms 🤗 — OIC Jade, Direk Andrei, and I (your Co-Direk) will gladly guide you through navigating STRAW Internal Affairs⚖️

TARA NAAAA!🌻

📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

P.S. sorry na po sa na blur ko🥹👉🏻👈🏻 u will and are missed po hehehehehe

message.text:
“Pang matalino lang diyan, kinakabahan ako!” 😣

Hi IABF!🌞 STRAW Internal Affairs can sound intimidating at first — lalo na kapag narinig mo na connected kami with the House of Representatives, Congress, plus petition writing and resolutions 😳.

Pero real talk? Once I joined, I realized na kung gaano karami ang terminologies, ganoon din karami ang platforms where we can lobby, voice out, and address our concerns within the campus.

To be honest, joining my home division was one of the best decisions I’ve ever made. I came in as a freshie with zero knowledge, pero my seniors, Direks, and OICs guided me every step of the way. It turned out not just manageable — but actually fun to serve and help the rest of the IABF community🥹🫶🏻

Kaya naman if you’ve been thinking about it… this is your sign 👀✨ JOIN US!
We’ll be here to welcome you with open arms 🤗 — OIC Jade, Direk Andrei, and I (your Co-Direk) will gladly guide you through navigating STRAW Internal Affairs⚖️

TARA NAAAA!🌻

📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

P.S. sorry na po sa na blur ko🥹👉🏻👈🏻 u will and are missed po hehehehehe

message.text:
“Pang matalino lang diyan, kinakabahan ako!” 😣

Hi IABF!🌞 STRAW Internal Affairs can sound intimidating at first — lalo na kapag narinig mo na connected kami with the House of Representatives, Congress, plus petition writing and resolutions 😳.

Pero real talk? Once I joined, I realized na kung gaano karami ang terminologies, ganoon din karami ang platforms where we can lobby, voice out, and address our concerns within the campus.

To be honest, joining my home division was one of the best decisions I’ve ever made. I came in as a freshie with zero knowledge, pero my seniors, Direks, and OICs guided me every step of the way. It turned out not just manageable — but actually fun to serve and help the rest of the IABF community🥹🫶🏻

Kaya naman if you’ve been thinking about it… this is your sign 👀✨ JOIN US!
We’ll be here to welcome you with open arms 🤗 — OIC Jade, Direk Andrei, and I (your Co-Direk) will gladly guide you through navigating STRAW Internal Affairs⚖️

TARA NAAAA!🌻

📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

P.S. sorry na po sa na blur ko🥹👉🏻👈🏻 u will and are missed po hehehehehe
